		NOTE COMPUTE PLAYER SCORES FOR HEARTS GAMES
		READ P1HEARTS, P2HEARTS
		IF P1HEARTS EQL 13
			THEN GO TO P1HASALL
			ELSE GO TO TEST2
TEST2		IF P2HEARTS EQL 13
			THEN GO TO P2HASALL
			ELSE GO TO NOSWEEP
P1HASALL	LET P2SCORE = 13
		GO TO SCOREPAD
P2HASALL	LET P1SCORE = 13
		GO TO SCOREPAD
NOSWEEP		LET P1SCORE = P1HEARTS
		LET P2SCORE = P2HEARTS
SCOREPAD	WRITE P1SCORE, P2SCORE
		STOP

*DATA		P1HEARTS = 5, P2HEARTS = 8
